title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 6 2022

description:
Boris Johnson speaks out against biological males in female sports, why won't Biden? Clay gets Dude Candle gifts for his birthday. He questioned men buying scented candles in the past, so the staff gifted him Dude Candle real-life scents, including "Sawdust," "Beer Fest," "Motor Oil," and "Aged Bourbon." Betsy DeVos, Education Secretary for President Trump, joins Clay and Buck to discuss Biden's radical Title IX plan to kill women's sports. C&B take calls.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
